@startuml
actor Customer
participant ReservationController
participant ReservationService
participant ScreeningRepository
participant ReservationRepository
participant TicketRepository

Customer -> ReservationController : POST /reservations
ReservationController -> ReservationService : createReservation(request)

ReservationService -> ScreeningRepository : findById(screeningId)
ScreeningRepository --> ReservationService : Screening

ReservationService -> ReservationService : checkSeatAvailability()
ReservationService -> ReservationRepository : save(reservation)
ReservationRepository --> ReservationService : Reservation

ReservationService -> TicketRepository : save(ticket)
TicketRepository --> ReservationService : Ticket

ReservationService --> ReservationController : reservation created
ReservationController --> Customer : 201 Created
@enduml